<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>GOD IS LOVE</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Pathien hehpihna a vak hi,
 I chiehna lampi chengah;
 Lungkham ei nem, gikpuok ei dawn,
 Pathien hehpih vak ahi!

[V2]
 Pathien hehpih vak ahi,
 Pathien hehpih vak ahi!
 2. Hun kidang, thil a kitheng zel!

[V3]
 Mihing thi'n hun a bei hi;
 Mahleh A hehpih dang ngeilo,
 Pathien hehpih vak ahi.

[V4]
 3. Hun thim pena kilang ale,
 A phatna danglo lang ding;
 Dah lai inle a vak lang zing,
 Pathien hehpih vak ahi!</lyrics>
<hymn_number>78</hymn_number>
</song>